Carole Madeleine Kaboud Mebam (amụrụ na 17 Septemba na afọ 1978) bụ onye Cameroon na-eme egwuregwu nke maara nke ọma na 100 na 400 mita mgbochi.
O nwekwara ihe ndekọ mba na 4 × 400 mita relay na 3:27.08 nkeji, ya na ndị otu Mirelle Nguimgo, Delphine Atangana na Hortense Béwouda nwetara n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ afọ 2003 na Paris.
